                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-12 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                <div class="single-service">
                    <div class="main-icon">
                        <i class="lni lni-book"></i>
                    </div>
